text: The St. John's IceCaps were an American Hockey League (AHL) team based in St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada. Previously the team was the Manitoba Moose and played in Winnipeg, Manitoba. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:2011 establishments in Canada Category:American Hockey League teams Category:Ice hockey teams in Canada Category:St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador
